      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) must agree with experimental measurements within ±20% across all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "NIH predictions compared against published FDA pump experimental data across all 5 flow-speed combinations. Maximum deviation of 14.3% observed at the 6 L/min, 2500 RPM operating point. All other points within 10%. Aggregate RMS error 8.7%. Output comparison criterion satisfied."
    },
    {
